WorkItem.Description:
I have been getting this error


Strict Standards: Declaration of FPDF_TPL::Image() should be compatible with FPDF::Image($file, $x = NULL, $y = NULL, $w = 0, $h = 0, $type = '', $link = '') in C:\xampp\htdocs\Pdfmerge\fpdi\fpdf_tpl.php on line 409

Please help

Comments.Message:
The arguments need to match exactly between the Image() in fpdf_tpl.php and the Image() in fpdf.php.   

In fpdf_tpl.php change line 269 to be: 
function Image($file, $x=null, $y=null, $w=0, $h=0, $type='', $link='',$align='', $resize=false, $dpi=300, $palign='', $ismask=false, $imgmask=false, $border=0) {

and in fpdf.php change line 898 to be the same thing.  This notice will go away.
I know the initial request is old, but I just found this class and needed to use it - was getting the same error and worked through it.  Hope it helps someone!
